│ a higher cost. The assertion `VPlan cost model and legacy cost model disagreed` fires because the function `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications`, which is meant to account for such   │
│ valid discrepancies, does not check for the elimination of dead recurrences.                                                                                                             │
